    <!--Help Activity-->
    <string name="title_activity_help">Help</string>
    <string name="help_title1">Principle</string>
    <string name="help_content1">ReadBoard is a reading challenge. Depending on your reading ability, choose the level that best suits you. The application will offer an appropriate number of categories. A category is a kind of theme including a description and suggestions of books.</string>
    <string name="help_title2">Goal</string>
    <string name="help_content2">The goal is to read a book that corresponds to each type of challenge ! As soon as the book you have finished your book, validate the associated category. You can help you with various suggestions made ​​to you. Feel free to suggest a new book suggestion to help others in their challenge.</string>
    <string name="help_title3">Features</string>
    <string name="help_content3">You can check your progress in order to know the number of categories to read and the percentage of completion.
You can share your progress with friends or a selected category you just read !
You can change the level at any time. The categories already read are always saved.
By clicking on the suggestions of books you will be redirected to an Amazon search on selected book.</string>


